Package: myRfunc
Title: Custom Themes for Various Table Packages in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jimmy",
           family = "Chen",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "your.email@example.com")
Description: Provides custom themes and utilities for various table packages in R,
    including gt, gtsummary, huxtable, flextable, and openxlsx. Features include
    consistent styling options, export capabilities, and professional-looking
    table formatting across different output formats.
